                        "difficultyIds": "a0f7d178f7b728b8bba7ef20ddeca62d",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Evaluating 评价",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nTSE would be performed every month. Small lumps or abnormalities needs to be reported. The spermatic cord finding (option 4) is normal. After a warm bath or shower, the scrotum is relaxed, making it easier to perform TSE.",
